WEBVTT

00:02.434 --> 00:04.334
You're special, Ellen...

00:04.370 --> 00:06.303
but that'll only make the fall harder.

00:06.371 --> 00:08.172
Once Patty meets you, there's no

00:08.173 --> 00:09.672
turning back.

00:09.673 --> 00:11.573
And she'll own you.

00:12.675 --> 00:14.476
No, I like Ellen.

00:14.477 --> 00:15.843
I think she's going to have

00:15.844 --> 00:17.979
a brilliant future.

00:18.047 --> 00:19.114
Working for Patty

00:19.115 --> 00:20.815
has taught me something about

00:20.816 --> 00:22.216
being a woman...

00:22.217 --> 00:24.653
You know what I'm in
the mood for? A fight.

00:24.654 --> 00:26.455
Your breach of trust...

00:26.456 --> 00:27.989
a professional

00:27.990 --> 00:30.225
You step in the ring with that woman,

00:30.226 --> 00:32.460
she will cut your balls off
and jam them down your throat.

00:32.461 --> 00:36.131
I don't like the way you do business,
but I get that it's necessary.

00:36.132 --> 00:39.668
Seeing how she balances
work and her personal life...

00:39.669 --> 00:42.572
People either leave you or they die.

00:42.573 --> 00:45.007
Those are the only two
endings possible with you.

00:45.008 --> 00:46.742
Get the hell out!

00:46.743 --> 00:49.211
What she prioritizes,
how she prioritizes...

00:49.212 --> 00:52.515
There's a difference between you and me.

00:52.583 --> 00:55.551
This isn't personal, Ellen.

00:55.552 --> 00:59.288
You've got to let things
just roll off your back.

00:59.289 --> 01:02.457
You are so full of shit, Patty.

01:02.458 --> 01:07.595
People like you and me, we only have
two options: forgiveness... revenge.

01:07.663 --> 01:10.298
I hope you know what you're doing.

01:10.299 --> 01:13.301
She's nothing less than
an inspiration to me.

01:16.638 --> 01:20.107
That's okay.

01:20.175 --> 01:24.444
I lied, too.

01:28.715 --> 01:32.050
No!

